Visualize your Bubble.io database schema effortlessly with BubVisch. Secure, private, and easy to use.

Schema Visualization:
Instantly visualize your Bubble.io database schema with BubVisch. Understand your database structure and relationships at a glance, enhancing your development efficiency.

Real-Time Updates:
Keep your database schema visual up to date in real-time. Any changes made in Bubble.io are immediately reflected in BubVisch, ensuring you always have the most current view.

Privacy and Security:
BubVisch prioritizes your data privacy and security. No database or JSON data is stored, guaranteeing complete confidentiality and peace of mind.

Seamless Integration:
Integrate BubVisch effortlessly with your Bubble.io workspace via our Chrome extension. Start visualizing your database schema with minimal setup and configuration.

User-Friendly Interface:
Enjoy a simple and intuitive interface that makes database visualization easy. No complex settings or technical expertise required to get started.

Subscription-Based Access:
Gain full access to all BubVisch features with a subscription for just 8 EUR per month. Cancel anytime through your account settings.

Comprehensive Support:
Access helpful resources and support directly from the extension. Find documentation, tutorials, and get assistance to maximize your BubVisch experience.

Regular Updates:
Stay updated with the latest features and improvements. Enable automatic updates to ensure you are always using the newest version of BubVisch.
